he%20first%20former%20or%20serving%20president%20to%20be%20the%20target%20of%20multiple%20criminal%20indictments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20ouster%20of%20a%20speaker%20in%20the%20House's%20234-year%20history%20was%20supported%20by%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20right-wing%20Republican%20hardliners.%20However%2C%20the%20House%20is%20almost%20evenly%20divided%20and%20with%20Democrats%20joining%20eight%20rebel%20Republicans%20rather%20than%20riding%20to%20McCarthy's%20rescue%2C%20he%20had%20no%20way%20to%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2058-year-old%20former%20entrepreneur%20--%20who%20did%20not%20comment%20as%20he%20left%20the%20chamber%20--%20had%20sparked%20fury%20among%20conservatives%20when%20he%20passed%20a%20bipartisan%20stopgap%20funding%20measure%20at%20the%20weekend%20backed%20by%20the%20White%20House%20to%20avert%20a%20government%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFlorida%20conservative%20Matt%20Gaetz%2C%20who%20forced%20the%20removal%20vote%2C%20gambled%20that%20he%20could%20oust%20McCarthy%20with%20just%20a%20few%20Republicans%2C%20helped%20by%20Democrats%20loath%20to%20bail%20out%20a%20speaker%20who%20only%20recently%20opened%20a%20highly%20politicized%20impeachment%20inquiry%20into%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20were%20warned%20by%20their%20leadership%20about%20plunging%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Binto%20chaos%26quot%3B%20but%20Gaetz%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20complained%20about%20McCarthy%20failing%20to%20honor%20agreements%20made%20with%20conservatives%2C%20retorted%3A%20%26quot%3BChaos%20is%20Speaker%20McCarthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20went%20down%20today%20is%20because%20nobody%20trusts%20Kevin%20McCarthy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20after%20the%20vote.%20%26quot%3BKevin%20McCarthy%20has%20made%20multiple%20contradictory%20promises%2C%20and%20when%20they%20all%20came%20due%2C%20he%20lost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDemocrats%2C%20too%2C%20had%20no%20love%20for%20McCarthy%2C%20pointing%20to%20his%20decision%20to%20renege%20on%20a%20deal%20with%20Biden%20on%20spending%20limits%20agreed%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20high-stakes%20talks%20over%20the%20federal%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Pigsty%20of%20incompetence'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Democrat%20Coalition%2C%20a%20bloc%20of%20pro-business%20Democratic%20lawmakers%2C%20described%20McCarthy%20as%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20not%20trustworthy.%26quot%3B%20And%20Congressional%20Progressive%20Caucus%20chairwoman%20Pramila%20Jayapal%2C%20a%20leading%20leftist%2C%20vowed%20to%20let%20Republicans%20%26quot%3Bwallow%20in%20their%20pigsty%20of%20incompetence%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20rescue%20McCarthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20came%20two%20days%20after%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%20passed%20a%20measure%20to%20avert%20a%20costly%20government%20shutdown%20--%20both%20with%20big%20bipartisan%20majorities%20--%20by%20extending%20federal%20funding%20through%20mid-November.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConservatives%20were%20furious%2C%20seeing%20their%20chances%20dashed%20for%20forcing%20massive%20budget%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20accused%20McCarthy%20of%20a%20flip-flop%2C%20saying%20he'd%20promised%20an%20end%20to%20hastily%20prepared%20stopgap%20legislation%2C%20hammered%20out%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20a%20return%20to%20budgeting%20through%20the%20committee%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%20after%20Democratic%20House%20Minority%20Leader%20Hakeem%20Jeffries%20encouraged%20his%20members%20to%20oust%20McCarthy.%20Every%20Democrat%20then%20joined%2011%20rebel%20Republicans%20to%20reject%20a%20preliminary%20motion%20that%20would%20have%20blocked%20the%20final%20ouster%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20McCarthy%20out%2C%20a%20temporary%20speaker%20put%20the%20House%20into%20recess%20until%20a%20permanent%20replacement%20is%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20will%20gather%20at%206