ed%20by%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20dark%20year%20in%20India%20for%20those%20who%20stand%20for%20a%20free%20press.%20The%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%20ranks%20India%20at%20161%2C%20in%20the%20bottom%20twenty%20of%20the%20180%20countries%20whose%20status%20it%20assesses.%20The%20fall%20has%20been%20immense%20and%20sharp%20since%202015.%20India%20is%20also%20the%20global%20internet%20shutdown%20capital%2C%20with%20by%20far%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20internet%20closures%20per%20year%20amongst%20all%20democracies.%20India%20has%20displayed%20record%20democratic%20backsliding%2C%20and%20the%20state%20of%20the%20press%20is%20a%20vital%20component%20of%20the%20deterioration.%20Unless%20he%20means%20it%20ironically%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20still%20never%20fails%20to%20talk%20about%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20straight%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attempt%20to%20tighten%20the%20noose%20around%20digital%20and%20independent%20media%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20single%20press%20conference%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20a%20withering%20Right%20to%20Information%20regime%20and%20the%20growing%20official%20culture%20of%20opacity%20has%20had%20a%20corrosive%20effect%20on%20our%20democracy.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20free%20run%20that%20purveyors%20of%20hate%20%E2%80%93%20pretending%20to%20be%20TV%20news%20channels%20%E2%80%93%20have%20despite%20Supreme%20Court%20strictures%20on%20hate%20speech%2C%20is%20poisoning%20the%20public%20sphere%20and%20enabling%20violence%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20a%20free%20press%20in%20a%20democracy%20cannot%20be%20overstated.%20It%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20is%20always%20under%20scrutiny%2C%20is%20answerable%20and%20accountable%20to%20the%20people%20who%20elect%20it.%20It%20is%20also%20to%20provide%20good%20and%20authentic%20information%20to%20citizens.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20a%20country%E2%80%99s%20media%20ends%20up%20deciding%20how%20informed%20its%20citizens%20are%20and%20how%20good%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20democracy%20is.%20Journalism%20is%20about%20speaking%20truth%20to%20power%2C%20and%20no%20democracy%20can%20survive%20if%20it%20needs%20superheroes%20to%20choose%20that%20vocation.%20As%20Bertolt%20Brecht%20reminded%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnhappy%20is%20the%20land%20that%20breeds%20no%20hero!%20No%2C%20%E2%80%A6unhappy%20is%20the%20land%20that%20needs%20a%20hero.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Raiding%E2%80%99%20an%20entire%20media%20organisation%20and%20snatching%20the%20electronic%20devices%20of%20journalists%20without%20due%20process%20is%20a%20bad%20omen%20for%20a%20free%20press%20but%20a%20worse%20signal%20for%20the%20continuation%20of%20democracy.%20All%20Indians%20should%20be%20alarmed%20about%20what%20independent%20journalists%20are%20enduring%20under%20an%20increasingly%20authoritarian%20dispensation%20because%20the%20ensuing%20darkness%20will%20eventually%20cast%20its%20shadow%20across%20their%20threshold%20too.%20The%20time%20for%20worry%20and%20concern%20is%20long%20over.%20If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20hear%20the%20alarm%20bells%20ringing%20loudly%2C%20you%20are%20either%20deaf%20%E2%80%93%20or%20pretending%20to%20be%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696385496000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FThe-Wire-Editorial-Logo-1024x495.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fterrorising-journalism-editorial%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Raiding%E2%80%99%20an%20entire%20media%20organisation%20and%20snatching%20the%20electronic%20devices%20of%20journalists%20without%20due%20process%20is%20a%20bad%20omen%20for%20a%20free%20press%20but%20a%20worse%20signal%20for%20the%20continuation%20of%20democracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.i