ing%20of%20the%20SP80%20boat%20being%20pulled%20by%20a%20kite%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20SP80%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20talked%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20over%20the%20week%2C%20and%20they%20were%20all%20amazed%20that%20it%20was%20a%20sailboat%20with%20no%20engine%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20Manon%20said%20of%20the%20yacht%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManon%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20Monaco%20said%20it%20looked%20more%20like%20a%20submarine%20or%20an%20airplane%2C%20and%20someone%20even%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20drone!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20company%2C%20started%20by%20pals%20Mayeul%20van%20den%20Broek%2C%20Xavier%20Lepercq%2C%20and%20Benoit%20Gaudiot%20in%202018%2C%20hopes%20to%20use%20its%20analog%20tech%20to%20reach%2080%20knots%2C%20or%2092%20mph%2C%20and%20shatter%20the%2065.45-knot%20record%20held%20by%20Paul%20Larsen%20and%20his%20Vestas%20Sailrocket%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuxury%20watchmaker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frichard-mille-ferrari-watch-is-worlds-thinnest-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERichard%20Millie%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20for%20its%20collaborations%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.richardmille.com%2Ffriends-and-partners%2Fmclaren-f1-team%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFormula%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecame%20SP80's%20title%20partner%20to%20support%20the%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20team's%20four-year%20investment%20in%20the%20project%2C%20the%20boat%20itself%20is%20still%20in%20early%20testing%20phases.%20The%20boat%20touched%20water%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20early%20August%20at%20Lake%20Geneva%20and%20could%20withstand%20being%20pulled%20by%20a%20speedboat%20at%2030%20knots%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsp80.ch%2Flaunching-on-lake-geneva-for-the-sp80-boat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epress%20release%20on