-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried's%20criminal%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20otherwise%20plodding%20day%20of%20jury%20selection%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%2C%20several%20prospective%20jurors%20shared%20some%20of%20their%20feelings%20about%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20said%20that%20they%20or%20their%20family%20members%20had%20invested%20in%20cryptocurrency%20in%20general.%20All%20of%20them%20lost%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20potential%20juror%2C%20who%20was%20ultimately%20dismissed%2C%20said%20he%20would%20harbor%20bias%20in%20the%20case%20because%20he%20and%20his%20twin%20brother%20each%20experienced%20major%20financial%20losses%20after%20investing%20in%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20invested%20in%20crypto.%20I%20did%20lose%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20twin%20brother%20invested%20even%20more%20and%20it%20did%20finally%20ruin%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20potential%20juror%20said%20he%20believed%20he%20harbored%20a%20bias%20in%20the%20case%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Beverything%20negative%26quot%3B%20he's%20heard%20about%20the%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20I%20could%20be%20totally%20unbiased%20about%20crypto%20given%20the%20history%20and%20everything%20negative%20I've%20heard%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20US%20District%20Judge%20Lewis%20Kaplan%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrong%20feelings%20about%20cryptocurrency%2C%20Kaplan%20explained%2C%20weren't%20relevant%20in%20the%20case.%20Prosecutors%20allege%20that%20former%20billionaire%20Bankman-Fried%20defrauded%20customers%20and%20investors%20of%20FTX%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20he%20ran.%20He%20did%20this%20by%20commingling%20funds%20with%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%20he%20also%20controlled%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJurors%2C%20Kaplan%20said%2C%20would%20be%20tasked