ver%20his%20drive%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20at%20work%20for%2060%20hours%20straight%20and%20not%20think%20about%20anything%20else%26quot%3B%20versus%20spending%20time%20with%20Ellison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shorter%20list%20entitled%20%26quot%3BARGUMENTS%20IN%20FAVOR%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20said%20the%20pair%20had%20shared%20interests%2C%20he%20enjoyed%20talking%20with%20her%2C%20and%20listed%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20like%20fucking%20you%26quot%3B%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20sent%20the%20memo%20in%20response%20to%20a%20four-page%20message%20from%20Ellison%20in%202018%20in%20which%20she%20said%20her%20feelings%20for%20SBF%20%26quot%3Bconsume%20a%20ton%20of%20my%20brainspace%26quot%3B%20and%20addressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20issues%20the%20relationship%20could%20cause%20in%20their%20work%20life%2C%20according%20to%20Lewis.%20In%20the%20message%2C%20she%20listed%20some%20of%20her%20hang-ups%20with%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bconfusing%20signals%2C%20e.g.%20telling%20me%20that%20he%20felt%20conflicted%20about%20having%20sex%20with%20me%2C%20then%20having%20sex%20with%20me%2C%20then%20ignoring%20me%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20book%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BCaroline%20wanted%20a%20conventional%20love%20with%20an%20unconventional%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSam%20wanted%20to%20do%20whatever%20at%20any%20given%20moment%20offered%20the%20highest%20expected%20value%2C%20and%20his%20estimate%20of%20her%20expected%20value%20seemed%20to%20peak%20right%20before%20they%20had%20sex%20and%20plummet%20immediately%20after.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20risks%20noted%20in%20Bankman-Fried's%20pros%20and%20cons%20list%2C%20Ellison%20continued%20to%20pursue%20a%20relationship%2C%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison's%20lawyer%20declined%20to%20comment%20and%20Insider%20received%20an%20automated%20message%20from%20Bankman-Fried's%20lawyer%2C%20who%20was%20in%20court%20for%20jury%20s