h%20his%20potential%20speakership.%20Jordan%20appears%20to%20have%20everything%20he%20ever%20wanted%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20powerful%20House%20Judiciary%20Committee.%20The%20Ohio%20Republican%20is%20also%20a%20main%20figure%20in%20what%20McCarthy%20has%20unilaterally%20declared%20is%20an%20impeachment%20inquiry%20into%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Reporters%20have%20also%20detailed%20how%20McCarthy%20has%20spent%20years%20wooing%20Jordan%20after%20Jordan%20helped%20sink%20his%20disastrous%202015%20speakership%20bid.%20Jordan%20also%20spoke%20before%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EElise%20Stefanik%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elise%20Stefanik%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60944772f22c6b00185dcbef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Elise%20Stefanik%2C%20a%20New%20York%20Republican%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAndrew%20Harnik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Elise%20Stefanik%20rose%20to%20national%20fame%20during%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20impeachment.%20She%20was%20catapulted%20into%20House%20leadership%20after%20Republicans%20booted%20then-Rep.%20Liz%20Cheney%20from%20her%20post%20as%20the%20N0.%203%20House%20Republican%20over%20her%20repeated%20criticism%20of%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20Once%20a%20more%20liberal%20Republican%2C%20Stefanik%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20Trump%20supporters%20in%20the%20entire%20House%20Republican%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKevin%20McCarthy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224178%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F645b272fc726bc00196aacb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKevin%20McCarthy%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYep%2C%20he's%20still%20here.%20There's%20nothing%20preventing%20McCarthy%20from%20running%20for%20the%20speakership%2C%20again.%20He%20has%20said%20multiple%20times%20in%20recent%20days%20that%20parties%20should%20vote%20for%20the%20candidate%20who%20wins%20the%20most%20votes%20in%20their%20respective%20conferences.%20His%20plea%20for%20such%20norms%20went%20unanswered.%20Now%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20he%20can%20grind%20out%20another%20potentially%20days-long%20drama%20and%20if%20he%20can%20keep%20many%20of%20the%20above%20potential%20challengers%20from%20running%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20likely%20to%20happen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20member%20of%20Congress%20to%20be%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House.%20And%20yes%2C%20Gaetz%20did%20vote%20for%20the%20former%20president%20at%20times%20during%20the%20January%20debacle.%20Still%2C%20it%20is%20very%20unlikely%20Trump%20wants%20this%20job.%20He%20already%20holds%20a%20gigantic%20lead%20to%20retake%20the%20GOP%20presidential%20nomination.%20There's%20simply%20no%20reason%20to%20think%20he%20would%20want%20this%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20quasi-coalition%20government%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere's%20a%20joke%20in%20Washington%20that%20people%20come%20to%20the%20Capitol%20hoping%20to%20find%20out%20it's%20like%20Aaron%20Sorkin's%20%26quot%3BWest%20Wing%26quot%3B%20only%20to%20discover%20it's%20a%20mixture%20of%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Cards%26quot%3B%20and%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BVEEP.%26quot%3B%20The%20truth%20always%20being%2C%20that%20only%20in%20Sorkin's%20fictional%20Washington%20do%20you%20get%20things%20like%20a%20liberal%20president%20nominating%20a%20conservative%20Supreme%20Court%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20reason%20to%20expect%20that%20both%20parties%20agree%20to%20some%20quasi-power-sharing%20arr