workforce%20and%20generate%3C%2Fa%3E%2064%25%20of%20America's%20gross%20domestic%20product.%20While%20the%20study%20is%20originally%20from%201996%2C%20the%20figures%20are%20still%20widely%20cited%20by%20the%20SBA%20and%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20when%20discussing%20the%20economic%20influence%20of%20family%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20spoke%20with%20a%20family-business%20expert%20and%20a%20small-business%20owner%20about%20how%20to%20navigate%20issues%20in%20family-owned%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESet%20boundaries%20between%20family%20and%20work%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFamily-owned%20small%20businesses%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Blifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20Engle%20said.%20You%20have%20to%20set%20boundaries%20with%20your%20time%20and%20relationships%20to%20achieve%20your%20personal%20and%20business%20goals.%20You%20also%20have%20to%20take%20time%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Engle%20adjusted%20the%20Red%20Fox's%20hours%20of%20operation%20so%20it's%20closed%20one%20day%20a%20week%20and%20on%20holidays.%20This%20lets%20her%20have%20more%20time%20with%20her%20three%20children%20and%20gives%20employees%20more%20time%20with%20their%20families%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20have%20clear%20personal%20goals%20and%20structure%20your%20business%20to%20the%20best%20of%20your%20abilities%20to%20match%20those%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20clear%2C%20defined%20roles%2C%20job%20titles%2C%20and%20responsibilities%20for%20everyone%20in%20the%20business%20sets%20boundaries%20and%20holds%20people%20accountable%20for%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20business%2C%20Engle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Jennifer%20Pendergast%20in%20a%20white%20blouse%20and%20silver%20necklace.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6515f7c6c50dce00191363d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Pendergast%20is%20a%20family-enterprise%20consultant%20and%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20the%20Kellogg%20School%20of%20Management%20at%20Northwestern%20University.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Jennifer%20Pendergast%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFamily-owned%20businesses%20blend%20family%20and%20workplace%20dynamics%2C%20so%20%26quot%3Bthe%20more%20clarity%20that%20there%20can%20be%20around%20expectations%20is%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Jennifer%20Pendergast%2C%20a%20family-enterprise%20consultant%20and%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kellogg.northwestern.edu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKellogg%20School%20of%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Northwestern%20University%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20should%20establish%20value%20statements%20and%20employment%20policies%20to%20remove%20any%20sense%20of%20favoritism%20and%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20among%20all%20employees%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearn%20to%20handle%20conflict%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConflict%20is%20inevitable%20in%20a%20family%20business%2C%20and%20Pendergast%20said%20it's%20crucial%20to%20set%20up%20processes%20for%20dealing%20with%20it%2C%20such%20as%20creating%20a%20code%20of%20conduct%20or%20building%20skills%20to%20handle%20disagreements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20family%20meetings%2C%20have%20conversations%2C%20be%20open%20to%20putting%20tough%20things%20on%20the%20table%20as%20opposed%20to%20trying%20to%20pretend%20that%20you're%20getting%20along%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20through%20issues%20usually%20resolves%20them%20quickly%2C%20Engle%20said.%20She%20encourages%20her%20team%20to%20openly%20discuss%20problems%20and%20new%20ways%20of%20doing%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20issue%20is%20that%20there's%20a%20constant%20blur%20between%20family%20time%20and%20work.%20Engle's%20family%20often%20brings%20up%20aspects%20of%20the%20business%20when%20they're%20together%20outside%20work%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20always%20be%20a%20talking%20point%20amongst%20your%20entire%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20you%20have%20to%20accept%20from%20day%20one%20because%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20you%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20separate%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20a%20succession%20plan%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20family-owned%20small%20business'%20longevity%20depends%20on%20planning%20for%20the%20future%2C%20Pendergast%20says.%20According%20to%20SCORE%2C%2047%25%20of%20family%20business%20owners%20who%20plan%20to%20retire%20in%20five%20years%20don't%20have%20a%20successor%2C%20and%20two-thirds%20of%20businesses%20don't%20survive%20the%20transition%20from%20the%20first%20to%20the%20second%20generation%20of%20ownership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20shareholder%20agreement%20that%20outlines%20who%20can%20own%20the%20business%2C%20who%20can%20sell%20shares%2C%20and%20any%20constraints%20on%20ownership%20and%20stock%20will%20help%20avoid%20problems%20when%20a%20business%20owner%20retires%2C%20Pendergast%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20recommended%20establishing%20an%20advisory%20board%2C%20which%20can%20include%20outside%20members%20of%20the%20business%20community%2C%20to%20offer%20an%20%26quot%3Bobjective%20viewpoint%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20company's%20succession%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20budget%20to%20hire%20an%20attorney%20to%20help%20draw%20up%20legal%20documents%20for%20succession%20planning%20or%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20business%2C%20Pendergast%20suggested%20contacting%20business%20schools%20at%20local%20universities%2C%20local%20Small%20Business%20Administration%20offices%2C%20or%20your%20bank%20for%20free%20or%20low-cost%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20a%20small%20business%20thriving%20for%20as%20many%20generations%20as%20Engle's%20requires%20looking%20at%20the%20big%20picture%2C%20Pendergast%20said.%20It'll%20ensure%20you're%20happy%2C%20doing%20what%20you%20love%2C%20and%20carrying%20on%20your%20family's%20dream.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20a%20big%20goal%20in%20mind%20and%20discuss%20your%20preference%20or%20passion%20for%20how%20to%20make%20that%20goal%20achievable%20or%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Engle%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-business-conflict-resolution-tips-boundaries-succession-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696363702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6515f967c50dce0019136407%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-business-conflict-resolution-tips-boundaries-succession-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Family%20businesses%20inevitably%20encounter%20conflict.%20Resolution%20is%20possible%20if%20you%20set%20boundaries%20and%20have%20a%20succession%20plan%20in%20place%2C%20experts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Erica%20Sweeney)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-business-conflict-resolution-tips-boundaries-succession-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20Boy%2C%2010%2C%20Dies%20After%20Neck%20Gets%20Entangled%20In%20Rope%20Swing%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2010-year-old%20boy%20died%20after%20the%20rope%20of%20a%20swing%20knotted%20around%20his%20neck%20while%20he%20was%20playing%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Baran%20district%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20according%20to%20pol