pay%20for%20union%20demands%2C%20analyst%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20in%20red%20union%20t-shirts%20carry%20a%20Stand%20Up%20sign%20as%20they%20march%20throughout%20downtown%20Detroit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c5af342ecf94db476cf28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUAW%20President%20Shawn%20Fain%20marches%20with%20UAW%20members%20through%20downtown%20Detroit%20on%20September%2015%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EBill%20Pugliano%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EAuto%20companies%20could%20forgo%20stock%20buybacks%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20costly%20union%20demands%2C%20an%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EStrikers%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20companies%20have%20poured%20towards%20buybacks%20and%20dividends.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESome%20investors%20have%20expressed%20willingness%20to%20sacrifice%20stock%20repurchases.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%20the%20UAW's%20strike%20is%20resolved%2C%20addressing%20the%20union's%20demands%20is%20unlikely%20to%20come%20cheap%20for%20the%20Big%20Three%20automakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20the%20ask%3A%20a%2036%25%20general%20wage%20increase%20over%20a%20four-year%20contract%20and%20a%20return%20to%20traditional%20pensions%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20And%20that's%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20the%20companies%20have%20paid%20to%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SEC%20filings%2C%20GM%20spent%20%242.5%20billion%20on%20buybacks%20in%202022%2C%20while%20Ford%20spent%20%24484%20million.%C2%A0And%20since%202010%2C%20GM%20has%20said%20it%20repurchased%20%2414.2%20billion%20in%20stock%2C%20while%20Ford%20bought%20back%20%243.5%20billion%20in%20shares%20from%202012%20to%202022%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-09-26%2Finvestors-would-trade-gm-ford-stellantis-buybacks-to-end-uaw-strike%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20noted%20that%20Ford%20prefers%20to%20pay%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStock%20buybacks%20are%20usually%20a%20good%20sign%20for%20investors%2C%20raising%20share%20prices%20and%20signaling%20strong%20financial%20health.%20But%20for%20the%20UAW%2C%20it's%20a%20sign%20of%20sharing%20more%20profits%20with%20shareholders%20than%20workers.%20In%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20union's%20demands%20has%20been%20to%20pay%20%242%20per%20worker%20for%20every%20%241%20million%20companies%20spend%20in%20buybacks%20and%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20companies%20could%20sacrifice%20some%20of%20their%20buybacks%20in%20the%20near-term%20(for%20instance%20a%20quarter).%20Once%20a%20contract%20is%20completed%2C%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20payments%20made%20for%20signing%20bonuses%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20Edward%20Jones%20analyst%20Jeff%20Windau%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThese%20types%20of%20near-term%20hits%20to%20cash%20may%20require%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20a%20buyback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20buybacks%20and%20dividends%20are%20a%20use%20of%20cash%20that's%20available%20after%20companies%20invest%20in%20their%20businesses.%20If%20expenses%20go%20up%20significantly%20and%20don't%20allow%20for%20buybacks%2C%20then%20companies%20could%20be%20pressured%20during%20challenging%20economic%20environments%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20investors%20seem%20ready%20to%20sacrifice%20stock%20buybacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20probably%20a%20happy%20medium%20where%20you%20maybe%20can%20stop%20share%20buybacks%20for%20some%20time%20and%20share%20that%20equity%20with%20labor%20and%20not%20just%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Mulberry%2C%20a%20client%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Zacks%20Investment%20Management%2C%20which%20owns%20Ford%20shares%20and%20manages%20%2415%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-09-26%2Finvestors-would-trade-gm-ford-stellantis-buybacks-to-end-uaw-strike%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20last%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Patrick%20Kaser%2C%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20for%20Brandywine%20Global%2C%20which%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20GM%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%2454%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management%2C%20seemed%20unwilling%20to%20accept%20lower%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20dividend%20cut%20will%20be%20a%20very%20bad%20sign.%20Stopping%20or%20cutting%20them%20will%20really%20be%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20companies%20don't%20have%20extra%20cash%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Bloomberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStellantis%20declined%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20Ford%20and%20General%20Motors%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20strike's%20cost%20to%20carmakers%20is%20mounting.%20The%20first%20two%20weeks%20have%20seen%20a%20total%20economic%20cost%20%243.95%20billion%2C%20including%20direct%20wages%2C%20manufacturing%20losses%2C%20and%20supplier%20losses%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Anderson%20Economic%20Group%20consulting%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20the%20rolling%20strike%20expands%20to%20all%20UAW%20members%2C%20that%20could%20cost%20companies%20billions%20of%20dollars%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20be%20talking%2050%2C000%20to%2060%2C000%20vehicles%20per%20week%20if%20they%20went%20out%20on%20a%20full%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Windau.%20%26quot%3BThat%20translates%20to%20a%20couple%20billion%20dollars%20per%20week%20of%20sales%2C%20%242%20%5Bbillion%5D%20to%20%243%20billion%20dollars%2C%20potentially.%20Those%20are%20all%20items%20that%20have%20been%20impacting%20the%20overall%20performance%20of%20the%20stock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20stock%20has%20fallen%203.7%25%20since%20the%20strike%20began%2C%20and%20GM%20has%20dropped%204.6%25.%20Stellantis%20is%20up%200.1%25%20as%20expanded%20strikes%20didn't%20target%20any%20of%20its%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issues%20of%20the%20UAW%20strike%20are%20already%20affecting%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrick%20Anderson%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Anderson%20Economic%20Group.%20%26quot%3BNo%20company%20can%20stay%20in%20business%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20without%20earning%20enough%20money%20to%20pay%20all%20of%20its%20costs%20including%20its%20labor%20costs.%20And%20the%20auto%20industry%20is%20highly%20competitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-strike-automakers-stock-buybacks-dividends-gm-ford-stellantis-wages-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696363379000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c5ae32ce014759e73bd58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fuaw-strike-automakers-stock-buybacks-dividends-gm-ford-stellantis-wages-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20companies%20could%20sacrifice%20some%20of%20their%20buybacks%20in%20the%20near-term%20(for%20instance%20a%20quarter).%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asoni%40insider.com%20(Aruni%20Soni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fuaw-strike-automakers-stock-buybacks-dividends-gm-ford-stellantis-wages-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20at%20Thank%20You%20For%20Coming%20screening%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696362878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104140909%2Cimgsize-59192.cms%22%2C%22orig