s%20recount%20horrific%20details%20of%20neglect%20by%20the%20nursing%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20a%20two-year-old%20with%20a%20chronic%20heart%20problem%20has%20been%20moping%20the%20floor%20under%20his%20daughter's%20hospital%20bed.%20He%20narrated%20details%20of%20an%20allegedly%20irresponsible%20hospital%20staff%20and%20the%20shortage%20of%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20two-year-old%20daughter%20is%20here%20for%20nearly%20a%20week%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%20She%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20cardiac%20condition%20that%20requires%20a%20surgery.%20However%2C%20the%20girl%20is%20also%20suffering%20from%20pneumonia%20and%20the%20family%20came%20to%20this%20hospital%20to%20get%20her%20treated%20before%20they%20can%20go%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20headed%20for%20Mumbai%20but%20they%20asked%20us%20to%20treat%20the%20pneumonia%20first.%20So%2C%20we%20came%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20hospital%2C%20their%20agony%20only%20compounded.%20%26quot%3BNurses%20make%20us%20wait%20if%20we%20ask%20them%20to%20turn%20off%20the%20intravenous%20fluids.%20Sometimes%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20it%20ourselves.%20The%20nurses%20sit%20outside%20and%20are%20on%20their%20phones.%20They%20get%20angry%20if%20we%20ask%20them%20twice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20as%20I%20tried%20to%20insert%20the%20intravenous%20tube%2C%20a%20little%20amount%20of%20blood%20oozed%20out.%20Even%20then%20I%20could%20not%20get%20the%20nurses%20to%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20hapless%20father%20recounted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tell%20us%20when%20medicines%20are%20over%20and%20ask%20us%20to%20get%20it%20from%20outside%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20are%20not%20just%20procuring%20medicines%20from%20outside%2C%20they%20are%20also%20cleaning%20the%20area%20around%20the%20hospital%20beds%20of%20their%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cleaning%20staff%20ask%20us%20to%20clean%20under%20the%20beds%20and%20I%20have%20been%20doing%20that%20for%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanitation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20problems%20plaguing%20this%20hospital.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bathrooms%20here%20are%20dirty.%20Stale%20food%20is%20dumped%20there.%20There%20are%20machines%20in%20the%20hospital%20but%20they%20don't%20work.%20Patients%20are%20sent%20outside%20for%20tests%2C%20including%20MRIs%20and%20CT%20Scans%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20patient's%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThirty-one%20patients%20died%20at%20the%20state-run%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Government%20Hospital%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Nanded%20that%20made%20national%20headlines%20on%20Monday%20following%2024%20deaths%20in%2024%20hours.%20Among%20these%2031%20patients%2C%2016%20were%20infants%20or%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20condition%20of%20as%20many%20as%2071%20patients%20at%20the%20hospital%20is%20still%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20shortage%20of%20staff%20and%20medicines%20have%20been%20levelled%20against%20the%20hospital%20whose%20dean%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20said%20procurement%20did%20not%20happen%20as%20scheduled%20from%20the%20Haffkine%20Institute%20from%20where%20all%20government%20hospitals%20in%20the%20state%20buy%20their%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said%20his%20government%20has%20taken%20the%20deaths%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Nanded%20very%20seriously%2C%20and%20appropriate%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20a%20detailed%20inquiry.%20He%20denied%20that%20there%20were%20shortages%20of%20medicines%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deaths%20are%20unfortunate.%20We%20have%20taken%20the%20incident%20very%20seriously.%20An%20inquiry%20has%20been%20ordered%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20appropriately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20in%20the%20state%20on%20Monday%2C%20saying%20the%20%26quot%3Btriple-engine%20sarkar%20(of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20NCP)%20should%20take%20responsibility%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20less%20than%20two%20months%20after%2018%20patients%20died%20in%2024%20hours%20in%20August%20at%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20Hospital%20in%20Kalwa%20in%20Thane.%20Twelve%20of%20them%20were%20above%20the%20age%20of%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696360320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fsip8p9t_nanded-hospital-ground-report_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-nanded-hospital-no-drugs-no-tests-say-patients-families-on-maharashtra-hospital-horror-4447388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Outside%20the%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Nanded%20where%2031%20patients%2C%20including%2016%20newborns%2C%20have%20died%20in%2048%20hours%2C%20families%20recount%20horrific%20details%20of%20neglect%20by%20the%20nursing%20staff.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-nanded-hospital-no-drugs-no-tests-say-patients-families-on-maharashtra-hospital-horror-4447388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-nanded-hospital-no-drugs-no-tests-say-patients-families-on-maharashtra-hospital-horror-4447388%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-ground-report-nanded-hospital-no-drugs-no-tests-say-patients-families-on-maharashtra-hospital-horror-4447388%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Release%20dates%20of%20Vicky-Rashmika%2C%20Shahid-Kriti%20movies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2