20year.%20Of%20those%20arrested%2C%20551%20were%20men%20who%20married%20underage%20girls%2C%20351%20were%20family%20members%2C%20and%2014%20were%20marriage%20solemnisers.%20The%20districts%20of%20Dhubri%20and%20Barpeta%20had%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20arrests.%20The%20previous%20crackdown%20resulted%20in%20over%203%2C000%20arrests%2C%20with%20a%20total%20of%204%2C823%20people%20now%20arrested%20in%20Assam%20for%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MUKUT%20DAS%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F961-arrested-for-child-marriages-in-assam%2Farticleshow%2F104140669.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChina-Linked%20Entities%20Gave%20NewsClick%20Rs%2038%20Crore%26quot%3B%3A%20Police%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20levelled%20a%20series%20of%20strong%20allegations%20against%20NewsClick%2C%20whose%20founder%20and%20HR%20head%20have%20been%20arrested%20under%20a%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law.%20Sources%20in%20the%20force%20alleged%20the%20news%20portal%20received%20Rs%2038%20crore%20from%20entities%20linked%20to%20Chinese%20individuals%20and%20some%20of%20its%20funds%20were%20shared%20with%20activists%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20and%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20who%20are%20accused%20in%20other%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20investigation%20alleged%20that%20the%20news%20portal%20had%20received%20money%20for%20pro-China%20propaganda%2C%20the%20police%20carried%20out%20searches%20at%20the%20home%20of%20journalists%20linked%20to%20NewsClick%20at%20over%20100%20locations%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20and%20Mumbai%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20sources%20alleged%20NewsClick%20received%20Rs%2038%20crore%20from%20entities%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20Chinese%20individuals%20and%20the%20funds%20were%20used%20to%20influence%20pro-China%20content%20on%20the%20portal.%20They%20claimed%20Rs%209%20crore%20was%20received%20as%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20(FDI)%20through%20inflating%20share%20prices%20and%2029%20crore%20was%20received%20as%20fees%20for%20export%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20proof%20was%20submitted%20by%20NewsClick%20for%20exporting%20any%20services%20to%20foreign%20entities%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Fund%20Sharing%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20claimed%20that%20some%20of%20the%20funds%20collected%20by%20NewsClick%20were%20also%20shared%20with%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20and%20Teesta%20Setalavad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Navlakha%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad-Maoist%20links%20case%20in%202018%20and%20has%20been%20under%20arrest%20since%20then.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20allowed%20the%20journalist-activist%20to%20be%20placed%20under%20house%20arrest%20because%20of%20his%20deteriorating%20health%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Navlakha%20was%20among%20several%20activists%20who%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20inflammatory%20speeches%20made%20at%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20conclave%20held%20on%20December%2031%2C%202017.%20Police%20claimed%20that%20these%20speeches%20triggered%20violence%20the%20next%20day%20at%20a%20gathering%20near%20the%20Koregaon-Bhima%20war%20memorial%20near%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETeesta%20Setalavad%20was%20arrested%20in%20June%202022%20along%20with%20former%20Gujarat%20police%20chief%20RB%20Sreekumar%20and%20former%20IPS%20officer%20Sanjiv%20Bhatt%20for%20allegedly%20using%20her%20close%20associates%20and%20riot%20victims%20to%20file%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20fabricated%20affidavits%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20a%20view%20to%20unseat%20the%20establishment%20and%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20establishment%20and%20the%20then%20chief%20minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20July%20this%20year.%20The%20bench%20had%20questioned%20the%20motives%20and%20timing%20of%20Ms%20Setalvad's%20arrest%20and%20said%20it%20thought%20the%20case%20against%20her%20was%20suspect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENewsClick%20has%20not%20reacted%20to%20these%20charges%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Reactions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%2046%20individuals%20associated%20with%20NewsClick%20are%20under%20investigation%20by%20agencies.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%2037%20male%20suspects%20have%20been%20questioned%20at%20premises%2C%209%20female%20suspects%20have%20been%20questioned%20at%20their%20respective%20places%20of%20stay%20and%20digital%20devices%2C%20documents%20etc.%20have%20been%20seized%2Fcollected%20for%20examination.%20The%20proceedings%20are%20still%20ongoing%3B%20so%20far%2C%20two%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested%20-%20NewsClick%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEGI%20is%20concerned%20that%20these%20raids%20are%20yet%20another%20attempt%20to%20muzzle%20the%20media.%20While%20we%20recognise%20that%20the%20law%20must%20take%20its%20course%20if%20actual%20offences%20are%20involved%2C%20the%20due%20process%20has%20to%20be%20followed.%20The%20investigation%20of%20specific%20offences%20must%20not%20create%20a%20general%20atmosphere%20of%20intimidation%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20draconian%20laws%2C%20or%20impinge%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20the%20raising%20of%20dissenting%20and%20critical%20voices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20slammed%20the%20government%20over%20the%20raids.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20