%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66994420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66994420.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66994420.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kargil%20All%20Set%20For%201st%20Ladakh%20Key%20Polls%20Since%20Article%20370%20Was%20Scrapped%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDrass%2C%20the%20world's%20second-coldest%20inhabited%20place%2C%20is%20gripped%20by%20the%20election%20fever%20and%20preparations%20have%20been%20made%20for%20polling%20tomorrow.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Council%20elections%20in%20Kargil%20after%20Article%20370%20was%20scrapped%20and%20Ladakh%20was%20made%20a%20separate%20Union%20Territory%20(UT)%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20is%20a%20fight%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20a%20combined%20Opposition%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20Congress.%20Wednesday's%20vote%20is%20being%20looked%20at%20as%20a%20referendum%20-%20if%20the%20people%20have%20accepted%20the%20Centre's%20decision%20of%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Iqbal%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Drass%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWednesday's%20vote%20is%20more%20about%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20people%20than%20development.%20The%2073-year-old%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20porter%20with%20the%20Army%20for%2040%20years%2C%20including%20during%20the%20Kargil%20War%20in%201999.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20the%20people%20are%20feeling%20politically%20disempowered%20after%20Ladakh%20became%20a%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20elected%20MLAs%20or%20ministers%20here.%20The%20Hill%20Council%20has%20lost%20its%20authority%20after%20Ladakh%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory.%20Yet%20this%20election%20is%20important%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammad%20Iqbal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2085%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20the%2026%20seats%20in%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Council%2C%20Kargil.%20The%20BJP%20is%20contesting%20on%2017%20and%20supporting%20some%20Independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKargil%20has%20been%20a%20traditional%20stronghold%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20and%20the%20Congress%20was%20the%20main%20rival.%20Now%2C%20the%20opponents%20%C2%A0have%20entered%20into%20an%20alliance%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20powerful%20religious%20institutions%20-%20the%20Jamiat%20Ulema%20Kargil%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Islamia%20School%2C%20%C2%A0traditionally%20backing%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20and%20the%20Imam%20Khumaini%20Memorial%20Trust%20backing%20the%20Congress%20-%20are%20driving%20the%20politics%20in%20Kargil.%20And%20religious%20clerics%20have%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20campaigning%2C%20Jamyang%20Namgyal%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20urged%20people%20to%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance%20and%20called%20NC%20chief%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20a%20%26quot%3BYazid%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20figure%20of%20hate%20for%20the%20Shia%20Muslims%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Imam%20Hussain%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20Prophet%20Mohammad%2C%20in%20the%20battle%20of%20Karbala.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFarooq%20Abdullah%20didn't%20allow%20Muharram%20processions%20in%20Srinagar%20to%20mourn%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20Imam%20Hussain.%20It%20was%20the%20BJP%20which%20allowed%20the%20procession%20in%20Srinagar%20after%2034%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Namgyal%20said%20at%20an%20election%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Ladakh%20administration%20had%20denied%20the%20%26quot%3Bplough%26quot%3B%20symbol%20to%20National%20Conference%20candidates%20which%20led%20to%20a%20legal%20battle%2C%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20setting%20aside%20the%20Ladakh%20hill%20council%20polls%2C%20earlier%20scheduled%20for%20September%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20dismissed%20Ladakh%20administration's%20petition%20opposing%20the%20allotment%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bplough%26quot%3B%20symbol%20to%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20the%20Ladakh%20administration%20in%20a%20fresh%20notification%20announced%20that%20polling%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%204%20and%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hill%20council%20elections%20are%20important%20since%20they%20are%20held%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20rare%20political%20alliance%20between%20the%20Buddhist%20and%20Muslim%20groups%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20social%20and%20religious%20groups%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20forged%20an%20alliance%20opposing%20Ladakh's%20UT%20status%20and%20demanding%20full%20statehood%20and%20constitutional%20protection%20under%20the%206th%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696353900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fsoqadqsg_ladakh-key-polls_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-all-set-for-1st-ladakh-key-polls-since-article-370-was-scrapped-4447192%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drass%2C%20the%20world's%20second-coldest%20inhabited%20place%2C%20is%20gripped%20by%20the%20election%20fever%20and%20preparations%20have%20been%20made%20for%20polling%20tomorrow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-all-set-for-1st-ladakh-key-polls-since-article-370-was-scrapped-4447192%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-all-set-for-1st-ladakh-key-polls-since-article-370-was-scrapped-4447192%2F