580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Tuesday%20claimed%20that%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20proposed%20to%20join%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%202020%20but%20he%20rejected%20the%20offer%20because%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cdeeds%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20poll-bound%20state%E2%80%99s%20Nizamabad%20district%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20KCR%20made%20the%20offer%20after%20the%20muncipal%20elections%20to%20Hyderabad%20in%20December%202020.%20Because%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhyderabad-ghmc-municipal-pols-trs-secures-lead-bjp-makes-major-gains%5C%22%3Esplit%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20Bharata%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(then%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi)%20needed%20external%20support%20to%20win%20the%20mayoral%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20municipal%20election%2C%20he%20used%20to%20welcome%20me%20at%20the%20airport%20with%20garlands.%20But%20he%20stopped%20suddenly.%20Why%20did%20he%20suddenly%20become%20upset%3F%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20reason%20KCR%20doesn't%20look%20me%20in%20the%20eye!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%20in%20exchange%20for%20BJP's%20support%20in%20GHMC.%20There's%20no%20question%20of%20supporting%20BRS!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20also%20warned%20him%20against%20passing%20the%20baton%20to%20KTR.%20After%20all%2C%20we%20are%20a%20democracy%2C%20not%20a%20monarchy!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRzttSFnvC0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRzttSFnvC0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20