%201%2C047%20families%20fell%20into%20the%20BPL%20category%2C%20with%20only%2014%20families%20managing%20to%20move%20out%20of%20it.%20In%202021-22%2C%201%2C751%20new%20families%20were%20added%20to%20the%20BPL%20category%2C%20and%20only%20two%20families%20improved%20their%20status.%20In%202022-23%2C%20the%20BPL%20category%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20303%20families%2C%20with%20just%20one%20family%20escaping%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Hemant%20Kumar%20Shah%2C%20based%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20we%20assume%20an%20average%20of%20six%20members%20per%20poor%20family%20among%20the%2031.64%20lakh%20poor%20families%2C%20it%20implies%20that%20the%20BPL%20population%20in%20Gujarat%20totals%201%20crore%2089%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20indicating%20that%20approximately%20one-third%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696340666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F2824052844_aa09eee89b_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-third-of-gujarats-population-is-living-below-the-poverty-line-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202020-21%2C%201%2C047%20families%20fell%20into%20the%20BPL%20category%2C%20with%20only%2014%20families%20managing%20to%20move%20out%20of%20it.%20In%202022-23%2C%20the%20BPL%20category%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20303%20families%2C%20with%20just%20one%20family%20escaping%20poverty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-third-of-gujarats-population-is-living-below-the-poverty-line-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Family%20Refused%20to%20Vaccinate%20Me%20Against%20Polio%3B%20I%20Was%2010-Month-Old%20When%20I%20Stopped%20Walking%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated%20on%2031%20October%201984%2C%20the%20news%20sparked%20riots%20across%20India%20soon%20after.%20The%20night%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20innocent%20families%2C%20including%20that%20of%20a%2010-month-old%20baby%2C%20Shravan%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConfined%20in%20his%20village%20home%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20he%20had%20a%20fever%20so%20high%20that%20it%20could%20not%20be%20measured%20on%20any%20instrument.%20And%20due%20to%20the%20nationwide%20strike%2C%20his%20family%20could%20not%20take%20him%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospital%20which%20was%2020%20km%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20night%2C%20I%20lost%20movement%20in%20one%20of%20my%20lower%20limbs.%20My%20mother%20was%20scared%3B%20she%20had%20heard%20that%20many%20children%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20had%20been%20affected%20by%20polio.%20And%20her%20fears%20came%20true.%20By%20the%20second%20night%2C%20both%20my%20limbs%20stopped%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Shravan%20lost%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311261%2Fmumbai-shilpa-mehta-jain-affected-by-polio-becomes-ca-starts-scholarship-for-disabled-people%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eability%20to%20walk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20his%20parents%20took%20him%20to%20numerous%20hospitals%20and%20tried%20everything%20but%20the%20damage%20was%20irreversible.%20It%20was%20these%20hospital%20visits%20that%20motivated%20Shravan%20to%20pursue%20medicine%20and%20raise%20awareness%20of%20polio%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20chasing%20this%20dream%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disqualified%20from%20appearing%20for%20the%20Pre-Medical%20Test%20(PMT)%20due%20to%20the%2080%20percent%20disability%20in%20my%20lower%20limbs.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20the%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court.%20Through%20their%20interven