%2FIMG-20230518-WA0031.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174626%2FIMG-20230518-WA0031.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174626%2FIMG-20230518-WA0031-300x176.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174626%2FIMG-20230518-WA0031-1024x600.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174626%2FIMG-20230518-WA0031-425x250.jpg%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22703%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrabhat%20Gupta%20(with%20garland).%20Photo%3A%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20on%20July%208%2C%202000%20when%20Prabhat%20alias%20Raju%20was%20going%20to%20his%20shop%20from%20his%20house%20he%20was%20fired%20at%20on%20his%20temple%20and%20between%20his%20chest%20and%20abdomen.%20The%20Gupta%20family%20accused%20Teni%20and%20three%20accomplices%20of%20the%20murder.%20After%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20acquittal%20by%20a%20lower%20court%2C%20the%20case%20dragged%20on%20legally%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20full%20of%20adjournments%20and%20judicial%20delays.%20In%20May%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20HC%20finally%20pronounced%20its%20judgment.%20It%20upheld%20the%20trial%20court%20verdict%20and%20acquitted%20Teni%20for%20lack%20of%20evidence%20proved%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajeev%20Gupta%20was%20devastated%20by%20the%20decision.%20He%20says%20the%20HC%20overlooked%20evidence%20and%20witnesses%20that%20proved%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20guilt.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20not%20given%20up%20his%20resolve%20for%20justice.%20His%20SLP%20against%20the%20acquittal%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20up%20for%20hearing%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20on%20October%209.%20Gupta%20says%20he%20will%20not%20stop%20till%20he%20drags%20down%20Teni%20from%20his%20ministerial%20perch.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20stop%20fighting%20for%20justice.%20I%20was%20disappointed%20by%20the%20acquittal%20but%20haven%E2%80%99t%20given%20up.%20I%20will%20put%20myself%20on%20mortgage%2C%20seek%20donations%20but%20fight.%20My%20brother%20will%20not%20come%20back.%20But%20by%20getting%20justice%20I%20want%20to%20ignite%20hope%20for%20justice%20in%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20days%2C%20Tikonia%20witnessed%20a%20flurry%20of%20activities%20from%20both%20sides.%20On%20October%202%2C%20Teni%20was%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20a%20BJP%20karyakarta%20sammelan%20held%20in%20his%20ancestral%20village%20Banveerpur.%20Though%20his%20son%20Monu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20directed%20by%20the%20SC%20to%20not%20enter%20UP%20unless%20for%20his%20trial%20hearings%2C%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20event%2C%20his%20photo%20featured%20prominently%20on%20the%20banner%20put%20up%20for%20the%20meeting%20as%20well%20as%20on%20posters%20across%20the%20Nighasan%20area.%20Today%2C%20October%203%2C%20local%20farmers%20have%20organised%20a%20prayer%20meet%20and%20a%20Kabaddi%20competition%20in%20memory%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cshaheed%E2%80%9D%20farmers%20and%20journalist%20who%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flakhimpur-kheri-trial-could-take-up-to-5-years-uttar-pradesh-district-court-tells-sc%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Trial%20Could%20Take%20Up%20to%205%20Years%E2%80%99%3A%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20District%20Court%20Tells%20SC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExactly%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20an%20annual%20wrestling%20competition%20(dangal)%20was%20organised%20by%20Monu%20in%20the%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20ancestral%20village%20Banveerpur%20in%20memory%20of%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20father.%20Teni%20along%20with%20UP%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20were%20the%20main%20guests%20at%20the%20event.%20A%20helipad%20was%20constructed%20on%20the%20playground%20of%20the%20Maharaja%20Agrasen%20Inter%20College%20in%20Tikonia%20for%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20helicopter%20to%20land.%20However%2C%20protesting%20farmers%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20dug%20up%20the%20helipad.%20Maurya%20was%20forced%20to%20take%20the%20road%20and%20since%20protestors%20had%20blocked%20this%20particular%20route%2C%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20event%20escorted%20him%20to%20the%20event%20from%20an%20alternate%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20had%20been%20simmering%20with%20tension%20ever%20since%20Teni%20on%20September%2025%2C%202021%2C%20had%20provocatively%20warned%20the%20farmers%20agitating%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%2C%20later%20repealed%20by%20Modi%20before%20elections%20in%20Punjab%20and%20UP%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmend%20themselves%E2%80%9D%20or%20else%20he%20would%20not%20take%20more%20than%20two%20minutes%20to%20mend%20them%20himself.%20Teni%20also%20reminded%20the%20farmers%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98past%20record%E2%80%99%20before%20he%20was%20elected%20a%20public%20representative%2C%20which%20farmers%20interpreted%20as%20an%20open%20threat%20of%20violence%2C%20and%20said%20that%20he%20did%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20run%20from%20any%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174749%2FPSX_20231003_121751-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174749%2FPSX_20231003_121751-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174749%2FPSX_20231003_121751-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174749%2FPSX_20231003_121751-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678090%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScenes%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%20in%20Tikonia%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20on%20October%204%2C%202021%20a%20day%20after%20the%20farmers%20were%20mowed%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20against%20these%20comments%20that%20farmers%2C%20many%20of%20them%20Sikh%2C%20had%20gathered%20in%20Tikonia%20that%20day%20when%20three%20vehicles%2C%20including%20a%20Thar%20in%20which%20Monu%20was%20allegedly%20sitting%20with%20his%20aides%2C%20belonging%20to%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20private%20convoy%20ran%20over%20them%20mercilessly%20and%20without%20provocation.%20Farmers%20Lovepreet%20Singh%20(19)%2C%20Gurvinder%20Singh%20(18)%2C%20Daljeet%20Singh%20(35)%20and%20Nachattar%20Singh%20(55)%20were%20killed.%20A%20local%20scribe%20who%20was%20covering%20the%20protest%2C%20Raman%20Kashyap%20(32)%2C%20was%20also%20mowed%20down%20by%20the%20speeding%20SUVs.%20Several%20others%20were%20injured.%20The%20outraged%20farmers%20allegedly%20lynched%20to%20death%20two%20BJP%20workers%2C%20Shubham%20Mishra%20and%20Shyam%20Sunder%2C%20and%20a%20driver%20Hari%20Om%20Mishra%2C%20in%20retaliation%20after%20the%20vehicles%20came%20to%20a%20halt.%20The%20farmers%20alleged%20that%20Monu%20and%20some%20of%20his%20aides%20fled%20into%20the%20fields%20on%20foot%20to%20escape%20the%20enraged%20mob%20and%20even%20fired%20shots%20at%20them%20and%20in%20the%20air%20with%20weapons.%20Initially%2C%20farmers%20had%20even%20alleged%20that%20one%20of%20the%20four%20farmers%20killed%20Gurvinder%20Singh%2C%20had%20been%20shot%20dead%20by%20Monu%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20escape.%20However%2C%20two%20autopsy%20reports%20of%20Gurvinder%20did%20not%20show%20any%20bullet%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMonu%20and%20his%20father%20Teni%20maintained%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20Tikonia%2C%20Monu%20was%20in%20Banveerpur%20village%20overseeing%20the%20wrestling%20competition.%20However%2C%20in%20a%205%2C000-page%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20court%2C%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20probing%20the%20incident%20last%20year%20said%20that%20Monu%20was%20present%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20violence.%20The%20SIT%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpre-planned%20conspiracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20oral%2C%20documentary%20and%20scientific%20evidence%2C%20the%20SIT%20also%20said%20that%20after%20running%20over%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20accused%20including%20Monu%20ran%20towards%20the%20sugarcane%20fields%20while%20firing%20from%20their%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20state%20government%20counsel%20while%20appearing%20in%20the%20HC%2C%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20the%20forensic%20report%20of%20the%20weapons%20recovered%20from%20the%20accused%20men%20corroborated%20the%20prosecution%20version%20that%20indiscriminate%20firing%20was%20done%20from%20the%20weapons.%20While%20Monu%20fired%20from%20his%20revolver%2C%20his%20rifle%20was%20used%20by%20co-accused%20Nandan%20Singh%20Bisht%2C%20said%20the%20SIT%20chargesheet.%20Another%20accused%20Sumit%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20was%20captured%20on%20video%20alighting%20from%20the%20Thar%20SUV%20after%20the%20vehicle%20lost%20control%2C%20allegedly%20fired%20from%20an%20illegal%20arm.%20The%20SIT%20also%20recovered%20one%20pistol%20from%20accused%20Ankit%20Das%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Babu%20Banarasi%20Das%3B%20one%20pump%20action%20gun%2012%20bore%20from%20Kale%20and%20one%20revolver%20from%20Satyam%20Tripathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENachattar%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20son%20Mandeep%20Singh%2C%20a%20paramilitary%20jawan%20serving%20on%20the%20borders%2C%20says%20even%20his%20family%20is%20yet%20to%20get%20the%20government%20job%20promised%20to%20them.%20He%20hoped%20his%20brother%20would%20get%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20got%20the%20government%20job%20yet%20or%20understood%20its%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fexclusive-time-wasted-due-to-vvip-visits-adg-prashant-kumar-on-lakhimpur-kheri-probe%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Time%20Wasted%20Due%20to%20VVIP%20Visits%E2%80%99%3A%20ADG%20Prashant%20Kumar%20on%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Probe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20work%20as%20an%20SSB%20jawan%20in%20early%202021%2C%20Mandeep%20did%20not%20get%20to%20see%20his%20father%20till%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20his%20post%20in%20Almora%20late%20on%20October%203%2C%202021%20and%20reach%20Tikonia%20the%20following%20day%20to%20attend%20the%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMandeep%2C%2027%2C%20is%20unhappy%20that%20Monu%20is%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20as%20he%20fears%20it%20could%20influence%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20FIRs%20registered%20in%20the%20incident.%20One%20by%20the%20farmers%20against%20Monu%20and%20others.%20The%20second%20by%20Sumit%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20BJP%20worker%2C%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20first%20case%2C%20against%20unknown%20farmers.%20The%20SIT%20had%20arrested%2013%20accused%20persons%20in%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20farmers.%20The%20name%20of%20the%2014th%20accused%20Virendra%20Shukla%20was%20added%20to%20the%20chargesheet%20under%20section%20201%20(causing%20disappearance%20of%20evidence).%20In%20May%202022%2C%20the%20HC%20said%20the%20SIT%20charge-sheet%20would%20reveal%20overwhelming%20evidence%20against%20the%20accused%20persons%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccommission%20of%20the%20offence%2C%20which%20has%20been%20termed%20cruel%2Cdiabolic%2C%20brutal%2C%20barbaric%2C%20depraved%2C%20gruesome%20and%20inhuman.%E2%80%9D%20The%20court%20had%20also%20noted%20that%20had%20Teni%20not%20made%20provocative%20statements%2C%20the%20Tikonia%20incident%20might%20not%20have%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20FIR%20regarding%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20BJP%20workers%2C%20charges%20have%20been%20framed%20against%20four%20farmers%2C%20Guruwinder%20Singh%2C%20Kamaljeet%20Singh%2C%20Gurupreet%20Singh%20and%20Vichitra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20only%20ten%20witnesses%20have%20appeared%20in%20the%20case%20against%20the%20farmers%20while%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20Monu%20and%20others%2C%20only%20four%20witnesses%20have%20been%20examined%2C%20said%20lawyers%20associated%20with%20the%20trial.%20The%20fifth%20witness%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20examined%20in%20court%20on%20October%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03175212%2FPSX_20231003_122121-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03175212%2FPSX_20231003_122121-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03175212%2FPSX_20231003_122121-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03175212%2FPSX_20231003_122121-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678091%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20body%20of%20one%20of%20the%20farmers%20in%20Tikonia%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20being%20taken%20away%20on%20October%204%2C%202021%20a%20day%20after%20four%20farmers%20were%20mowed%20down.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EPawan%20Kashyap%2C%2032%2C%20brother%20of%20scribe%20Raman%20Kashyap%2C%20says%20it%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20get%20justice%20till%20Teni%20remains%20a%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20powerful%20man%20and%20is%20moneyed.%20Justice%20bows%20to%20power.%20Till%20he%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20government%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20he.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPawan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparaikor%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20case%2C%20alleged%20the%20hearings%20are%20held%20under%20a%20tense%20atmosphere%20where%20people%20from%20the%20rival%20side%20gather%20in%20court%20in%20large%20numbers.%20This%20intimidates%20the%20witnesses%2C%20he%20alleged.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20witness%20sees%2015-20%20people%20in%20court%2C%20some%20with%20arms%2C%20even%20they%20get%20scared%20for%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaman%E2%80%99s%20death%20has%20made%20life%20difficult%20for%20the%20Kashyap%20family.%20His%20father%20stopped%20working%20after%20he%20got%20a%20heart%20ailment%20in%202016.%20Raman%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20brother%20Rajat%20Kashyap%20was%20running%20a%20small%20shop%20in%20Nighasan%20till%20COVID-19%20forced%20it%20to%20be%20shut%20down.%20Compounding%20the%20misery%20for%20the%20family%2C%20Rajat%20died%20in%20March%20this%20year%20after%20suffering%20from%20blood%20cancer.%20He%20left%20behind%20a%20young%20child.%20Raman%20himself%20left%20behind%20two%20young%20children%2C%20a%20son%20(5)%20and%20daughter%20(12).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPawan%20is%20now%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20in%20the%20family%2C%20putting%20him%20under%20tremendous%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20existence%20has%20been%20jolted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pawan%20says%2C%20stressing%20that%20whenever%20he%20steps%20out%20of%20his%20house%20his%20family%20is%20worried%20about%20his%20safety.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%99If%20something%20happens%20to%20me%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20three%20kids%E2%80%99%2C%20my%20family%20wonders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVinay%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20deceased%20farmers%2C%20says%20the%20trial%20is%20in%20evidence%20stage.%20Singh%20alleges%20that%20there%20was%20pressure%20being%20put%20on%20their%20witnesses.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20break%20our%20witnesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%20For%20instance%2C%20he%20said%20that%20in%20a%20recent%20hearing%2C%20when%20he%20felt%20that%20his%20witness%2C%20whose%20identity%20he%20did%20not%20reveal%2C%20was%20under%20pressure%2C%20he%20got%20an%20adjournment%20saying%20that%20the%20witness%E2%80%99%20mental%20condition%20was%20not%20right%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShailendra%20Kumar%20Gaur%2C%20lawyer%20for%20accused%20Ankit%20Das%2C%20however%2C%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20that%20the%20accused%20side%20were%20pressuring%20the%20witnesses.%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no%2C%20nothing%20like%20that.%20They%20(Ankit%20Das%2C%20Monu%20and%20others)%20appear%20in%20court%20only%20when%20there%20is%20a%20hearing.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flakhimpur-supreme-court-bail-ashish-mishra%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20in%20January%20while%20granting%20interim%20bail%20to%20Monu%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20UP%20and%20the%20NCT.%20Recently%2C%20the%20court%20modified%20its%20order%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20stay%20in%20NCT%20to%20take%20care%20of%20an%20ill%20family%20member.%20The%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20trial%20judge%20earlier%20this%20year%20informed%20the%20SC%20that%20the%20trial%20against%20Monu%20and%20his%20co-accused%20would%20take%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years%20to%20be%20completed.%20The%20case%20against%20Monu%20would%20have%20208%20oral%20witnesses%2C%20171%20documentary%20evidence%2C%2017%20scientific%20evidence%2C%207%20physical%20evidence%20and%2024%20forensic%20science%20laboratory%20reports%2C%20the%20prosecution%20proposed%20in%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bereaved%20farmers%20are%20mentally-prepared%20for%20the%20long-haul.%20However%2C%20Satnam%20Singh%20regrets%20the%20fact%20that%20Teni%20is%20still%20a%20minister%20and%20was%20not%20charged%20as%20a%20co-accused.%20He%20says%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20four%20farmers%2C%20which%20were%20kept%20on%20display%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%20the%20day%20after%2C%20should%20not%20have%20been%20cremated%20until%20Teni%20faced%20action.%20It%20must%20be%20recalled%20that%20amid%20a%20tense%20atmosphere%20in%20Tikonia%20where%20farmers%20had%20gathered%20with%20the%20bodies%20to%20start%20a%20long-drawn%20protest%2C%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20leader%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20had%20mediated%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20enraged%20farmers%20to%20diffuse%20the%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20bodies%20been%20kept%20at%20the%20site%20for%20just%20a%20day%20longer%2C%20the%20government%20would%20have%20been%20under%20pressure%20to%20act%20against%20Teni%20and%20force%20him%20to%20resign%2C%20says%20Satnam%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20farmer%20unions%20did%20not%20consult%20them%20before%20taking%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20dialled%20the%20phone%20numbers%20of%20district%20Magistrate%20Kheri%20Mahendra%20Bahadur%20Singh%20to%20ask%20him%20about%20the%20jobs%20promised%20to%20the%20kin%20of%20the%20farmers%20killed%20in%20Tikonia.%20But%20he%20could%20not%20be%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696336052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03174403%2FPSX_20231003_122551-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flakhimpur-kheri-trial-ashish-mishra-teni-trial-compensation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Families%20of%20those%20who%20died%20are%20willing%20to%20run%20the%20distance%2C%20that%20our%20legal%20system%20often%20asks%20of%20victims%2C%20for%20justice.%20But%20that%20alone%20has%20not%20been%20enough.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flakhimpur-kheri-trial-ashish-mishra-teni-trial-compensation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title