%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edidi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(referring%20to%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee)%20provide%20us%20with%20our%20money%3F%20We%20are%20going%20to%20Delhi%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20Modi%20the%20extent%20of%20our%20struggles%20caused%20by%20his%20actions.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKader%20is%20among%20the%20hundreds%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supporters%20currently%20agitating%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20MGNREGS%20and%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%20(PMAY)%20funds%20for%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20a%20strategic%20move%20by%20the%20party%20to%20shape%20a%20narrative%20highlighting%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20perceived%20neglect%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20rural%20hardship%20and%20the%20migration%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20from%20Bengal%20in%20search%20of%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20most%20recent%20round%20of%20%E2%80%98Duare%20Sarkar%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20concluded%20on%20September%2030%2C%20approximately%201.5%20million%20migrant%20workers%20registered%20at%20camps%20established%20throughout%20Bengal.%20Duare%20Sarkar%20is%20an%20outreach%20campaign%20initiated%20by%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20for%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Edelivery%20of%20some%20state%20government%20schemes%20at%20people%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps%2C%20conducted%20at%20gram%20panchayat%20and%20municipal%20ward%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CVillagers%20in%20Bengal%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20state%20due%20to%20non-payment%20and%20unavailability%20of%20the%20MGNREGS%20programme.%20Poor%20people%20are%20also%20being%20deprived%20of%20houses%20due%20to%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20discriminatory%20attitude%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Samirul%20Islam%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20newly%20formed%20West%20Bengal%20Migrant%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Board.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESafiq%20Sheikh%20from%20Nauda%20in%20Murshidabad%20joined%20the%20agitation%20hoping%20to%20be%20in%20the%20good%20books%20of%20the%20newly%20elected%20panchayat%20members%20in%20his%20area.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20getting%20old%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20to%20earn%20my%20living.%20If%20Modi%20releases%20the%20fund%2C%20work%20would%20again%20start%20under%20%5Bthe%5D%20100%20day%20job%20guarantee%20scheme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhunger-and-broken-promises-in-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3EOnce%20a%20Maoist%20Hotbed%2C%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%20Is%20Now%20Battling%20Hunger%20and%20Anger%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20these%20protesters%20is%20the%20grieving%20father%20of%20three%20young%20children%2C%20aged%20between%20three%20and%20five%2C%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fwall-collapse-kills-3-tribal-kids-triggers-tmc-bjp-row-over-narendra-modi-goverments-freeze-on-housing-funds%2Fcid%2F1970233%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhen%20the%20mud%20wall%20of%20their%20house%20collapsed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20incident%20took%20on%20a%20political%20dimension%20when%20Trinamool%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20attributed%20the%20tragedy%20to%20the%20non-payment%20of%20funds%20under%20the%20PMAY.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202021%2C%20the%20allocation%20of%20funds%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1041183%2Fwhy-the-centre-has-not-paid-mgnrega-wages-in-bengal-for-a-year%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20come%20to%20a%20halt%20due%20to%20a%20dispute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20it%20and%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20concerning%20alleged%20corruption%20by%20the%20latter%20in%20the%20MGNREGS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAjit%20Dolui%2C%20a%20labourer%20from%20Hooghly%2C%20shared%20his%20frustration%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20us%20villagers%20were%20tasked%20with%20cleaning%20the%20hospital%20grounds%20for%20a%20rally%20addressed%20by%20the%20chief%20minister.%20The%20panchayat%20also%20assigned%20us%20to%20repair%20a%20few%20things.%20However%2C%20when%20we%20asked%20for%20payment%2C%20they%20informed%20us%20that%20it%20was%20under%20the%20MGNREGS.%20It%20has%20been%20two%20years%2C%20and%20I%20have%20not%20received%20any%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20Delhi.%20I%20am%20disgusted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Delhi%20agitation%2C%20a%20brainchild%20of%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20and%20heir%20apparent%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20is%20also%20viewed%20as%20a%20platform%20to%20establish%20him%20as%20a%20prominent%20national%20leader.%20Abhishek%20has%20been%20actively%20participating%20in%20meetings%20of%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20INDIA%20bloc%20alongside%20his%20aunt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20teacher%20recruitment%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20August%202023%2C%20the%20ED%20conducted%20a%20raid%20at%20the%20office%20of%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20Leaps%20and%20Bounds%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20scam.%20He%20was%20also%20summoned%20by%20the%20agency%20for%20questioning%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Fed-summons-abhishek-on-sept-13-the-day-of-india-panel-meeting-8933877%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20last%20meeting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20consistently%20labelled%20these%20actions%20as%20political%20harassment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCentral%20discrimination%20has%20remained%20a%20burning%20issue%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20The%20Left%20used%20it%20to%20garner%20sympathy%20during%20their%20rule.%20Trinamool%20has%20taken%20the%20same%20tactics.%20Despite%20many%20instances%20of%20malpractices%20and%20corruption%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20use%20this%20as%20an%20election%20issue%20and%20might%20actually%20get%20people%E2%80%99s%20support.%20This%20will%20work%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20in%20the%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20political%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20West%20Bengal%20are%20very%20sensitive%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20MGNREGA%20and%20housing%20schemes%2C%20accusing%20the%20state%20government%20of%20issuing%2025%20lakh%20fake%20MGNREGS%20job%20cards%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20misappropriation%20of%20significant%20government%20funds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1963198%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20press%20release%20by%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20despite%20multiple%20requests%2C%20the%20state%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20comprehensive%20action%20taken%20report%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20withholding%20of%20funds%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%2C%202005.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%20(October%202)%2C%20Union%20rural%20development%20minister%20Giriraj%