ontent%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10154711%2FUntitled-design-2021-02-10T154651.122.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20opposition%20parties%2C%20condemning%20the%20raids%20on%20journalists%20connected%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberately%20persecuted%20and%20suppressed%E2%80%9D%20media%20organisations%20that%20speak%20truth%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20alliance%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfresh%20attack%20on%20the%20media%E2%80%9D%20compromises%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20standing%20as%20a%20mature%20democracy.%20%E2%80%9CIronically%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20paralysed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20journalists%20inciting%20hatred%20and%20divisiveness%20in%20the%20nation.%20In%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20it%20would%20behove%20the%20BJP%20Government%20to%20focus%20on%20genuine%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20people%2C%20and%20stop%20attacking%20the%20media%20to%20distract%20attention%20from%20its%20failures%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20the%20Delhi%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3Eraided%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20homes%20of%20several%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20The%20case%20was%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20about%20an%20American%20millionaire%20who%20allegedly%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%20to%20finance%20its%20propaganda%20worldwide.%20Subsequently%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%5C%22%3Ecited%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20report%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20claim%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStatement%20by%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20on%20BJP%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Fresh%20Attack%20on%20the%20Media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20parties%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%E2%80%99s%20fresh%20attack%20on%20the%20media.%20We%20steadfastly%20stand%20with%20the%20media%20and%20for%20the%20constitutionally%20protected%20freedoms%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20deliberately%20persecuted%20and%20suppressed%20the%20media%20by%20deploying%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20suppress%20the%20British%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%2C%20Newslaundry%2C%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%2C%20Bharat%20Samachar%2C%20the%20Kashmir%20Walla%2C%20The%20Wire%20etc.%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20the%20journalists%20of%20NewsClick.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20tried%20to%20convert%20the%20media%20into%20a%20mouthpiece%20for%20its%20partisan%20and%20ideological%20interests%20by%20facilitating%20the%20takeover%20of%20media%20organisations%20by%20crony%20capitalists.%20Both%20the%20government%20and%20its%20ideologically%20aligned%20organisations%20have%20resorted%20to%20reprisals%20against%20individual%20journalists%20who%20spoke%20truth%20to%20power.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20spearheaded%20regressive%20policies%20like%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%202021%20that%20constrict%20the%20media%20from%20reporting%20objectively.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20only%20hiding%20its%20sins%20of%20omission%20and%20commission%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20also%20compromising%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20standing%20as%20a%20mature%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20coercive%20actions%20are%20invariably%20directed%20against%20only%20those%20media%20organisations%20and%20journalists%20that%20speak%20truth%20to%20power.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20paralysed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20journalists%20inciting%20hatred%20and%20divisiveness%20in%20the%20nation.%20In%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20it%20would%20behove%20the%20BJP%20Government%20to%20focus%20on%20genuine%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20people%2C%20and%20stop%20attacking%20the%20media%20to%20distract%20attention%20from%20its%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJai%20Hind.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696326888000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10154711%2FUntitled-design-2021-02-10T154651.122.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffresh-attack-media-india-parties-condemn-raids-newsclick%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIronically%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20paralysed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20journalists%20inciting%20hatred%20and%20divisiveness%20in%20the%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffresh-attack-media-india-parties-condemn-raids-newsclick%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amita