20She%20became%20a%20data%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBody%20negativity%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20tends%20to%20resurface.%20During%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%202021%2C%20her%20insecurities%20resurfaced%20when%20she%20experienced%20a%20relationship%20break-up.%20She%20attributes%20it%20to%20her%20plus-sized%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20turmoil%20hampered%20her%20professional%20work%20and%20she%20started%20to%20journal%20to%20get%20out%20of%20that%20sinking%20feeling.%20Things%20took%20a%20dramatic%20turn%20when%20a%20modeling%20agency%20noticed%20her%20self-styled%20photos%20on%20Instagram%20and%20offered%20her%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20seasoned%20model%2C%20Sharma%20talks%20about%20how%20fashion%20has%20given%20her%20more%20than%20money%20could%20measure.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20made%20me%20appreciate%20myself%2C%20given%20me%20self-esteem%20and%20pride.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20a%20role%20model%20for%20many%20plus-sized%20women%20and%20I%20get%20messages%20where%20they%20say%20that%20they%20have%20been%20inspired%20to%20wear%20swimwear%20because%20of%20me%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125136%2Fkhushboo_2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125136%2Fkhushboo_2.jpg%20683w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125136%2Fkhushboo_2-200x300.jpg%20200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678005%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKhushboo%20Sharma.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20thriving%20in%20her%20newfound%20self-love%2C%20Sharma%20rues%20the%20fact%20that%20not%20enough%20is%20being%20done%20to%20increase%20the%20representation%20of%20alternate%20beauties%20in%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProper%20scouting%20is%20not%20done%20for%20the%20plus-sized%20community%2C%20and%20only%20the%20models%20who%20had%20begun%20the%20diversity%20movement%20end%20up%20getting%20all%20the%20spots.%20The%20new%20girls%20are%20hardly%20featured.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20attempt%20to%20build%20and%20empower%20a%20community%20for%20upcoming%20faces%20and%20the%20same%20faces%20keep%20getting%20the%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharma%20claims%20to%20have%20built%20a%20plus-sized%20community%20of%205%2C000%20women%20who%20aspire%20to%20work%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry.%20Sharma%20is%20also%20proud%20that%20her%20peers%20from%20her%20hometown%20have%20followed%20in%20her%20footsteps%20in%20owning%20their%20bodies%20and%20aspiring%20for%20a%20modelling%20career.%20%E2%80%9CBrands%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhouseofsoho.in%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3EHouse%20of%20Soho%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsajke.in%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3ESajke%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20some%20of%20my%20hometown%20brands%20featuring%20plus-sized%20models%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGlorification%20of%20beauty%20that%20often%20adheres%20to%20western%20standards%20leads%20to%20a%20huge%20section%20of%20insecure%20and%20neglected%20aspirants.%20India%E2%80%99s%20obsession%20with%20fair%20skin%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact.%20Due%20to%20pressures%20from%20a%20liberated%20feminist%20audience%2C%20Hindustan%20Unilever%E2%80%99s%20popular%20skin%20lightening%20cream%20%E2%80%98Fair%20%26amp%3B%20Lovely%E2%80%99%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffair-and-lovely-hindustan-unilever%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20rebrand%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20product%20to%20%E2%80%98Glow%20%26amp%3B%20Lovely%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20Gharu%2C%20a%20dusky%20beauty%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Jodhpur%2C%20has%20a%20similar%20story.%20She%20was%20greatly%20stirred%20when%20she%20saw%20the%202008%20Bollywood%20blockbuster%20film%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFashion_(2008_film)%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFashion%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20star-spangled%20movie%20directed%20by%20Madhur%20Bhandarkar%20that%20dealt%20with%20the%20darker%20sides%20of%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20industry%20and%20how%20models%20fight%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20I%20first%20saw%20tall%2C%20lanky%2C%20dark-skinned%20models%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gharu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20chasing%20her%20dreams%20across%20Jodhpur%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20finally%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20home%20to%20Bollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20years%20of%20gruelling%20hard%20work%20punctuated%20by%20painful%20rejections%20due%20to%20her%20dark%20skin%20tone.%20She%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20her%20mentor%20for%20counselling%20her.%20She%20was%20taught%20to%20first%20accept%20herself%20as%20beautiful%20before%20expecting%20recruiters%20to%20see%20the%20beauty%20in%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20every%20dark-skinned%20model%20out%20there%2C%20to%20love%20yourself%20and%20work%20hard%20%E2%80%93%20you%20will%20definitely%20succeed!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gharu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20fashion%20is%20still%20suffering%20from%20the%20patriarchal%20mindset%20where%20the%20male%20gaze%20allows%20only%20fair%2C%20slim%2C%20and%20tall%20models%20to%20be%20appreciated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20beauty%20standards%20in%20fashion%20are%20just%20the%20reflection%20of%20the%20beauty%20mindsets%20of%20all%20women.%20They%20are%20increasingly%20getting%20Botox%20to%20fix%20their%20noses%2C%20lips%2C%20faces%2C%20etc.%20They%20do%20it%20because%20they%20think%20it%20will%20earn%20them%20more%20love%20and%20%E2%80%98likes%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Geetanjali%20Adhikari%2C%20a%20model%20from%20Delhi%2C%20whose%20fashion%20journey%20is%20one%20from%20facing%20fat-shaming%20to%20gaining%20acceptance%20and%20ultimately%20achieving%20industry%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20consider%20myself%20very%20lucky%20for%20being%20a%20plus-sized%20model.%20The%20body%20I%20was%20stigmatised%20for%2C%20is%20now%20celebrated.%20But%20I%20feel%20sorry%20for%20the%20big%20curvy%20girls%20who%20are%20still%20struggling%20within%20their%20bodies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Ffashionably-queer-what-does-fashion-mean-to-indias-queer-persons%5C%22%3EFashionably%20Queer%3A%20What%20Does%20Fashion%20Mean%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Queer%20Persons%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETokenism%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Luna%2C%20a%20transgender%20model%20and%20drag%20queen%2C%20the%20concept%20or%20idea%20of%20fashion%20is%20inclusive%20but%20the%20business%20of%20fashion%20may%20not%20be%20so.%20She%20says%20that%20tokenism%20continues%20to%20exist%20in%20Indian%20fashion%20despite%20significant%20strides%20having%20been%20made%20in%20inclusion%20and%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20unfortunately%20has%20been%20run%20by%20men%20who%20have%20instilled%20their%20biases.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20am%20extremely%20thankful%20for%20social%20media%20because%20ten%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20imagined%20myself%20where%20I%20am%20today.%20I%20always%20thought%20fashion%20was%20not%20for%20me.%20Now%2C%20when%20I%20am%20in%20a%20room%20with%20people%20I%20have%20grown%20up%20idolising%2C%20it%20hits%20differently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToshada%20Uma%2C%20who%20is%204%E2%80%999%E2%80%9D%20tall%2C%20has%20lost%20count%20of%20runway%20shows%20she%20has%20walked%20while%20wearing%20shoes%20that%20are%202-4%20sizes%20above%20hers.%20Her%20height%20is%20well%20below%20the%20conventional%20average.%20She%20remembers%20how%2C%20on%20multiple%20instances%2C%20her%20colleagues%20asked%20her%20what%20she%20did%20for%20a%20living.%20It%20sounded%20like%20they%20doubted%20if%20she%20belonged%20to%20the%20same%20set%2C%20got%20the%20same%20pay%2C%20and%20worked%20the%20same%20hours%20as%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20makes%20one%20think%20if%20things%20would%20be%20any%20different%20if%20the%20industry%20hired%20diverse%20models%20not%20just%20for%20some%20brownie%20points%20but%20because%20they%20genuinely%20believed%20it%20was%20important%20to%20represent%20various%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20says%2C%20citing%20the%20common%20practice%20of%20tokenist%20inclusion%20versus%20an%20organic%20attempt%20to%20change%20the%20culture%20of%20recruiting%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharma%20considers%20the%20plus-sized%20fashion%20industry%20in%20India%20to%20be%20dysfunctional.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20clothes%20that%20are%20meant%20for%20us%20are%20unattractive%20and%20have%20no%20sense%20of%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20narrative%20that%20attempts%20to%20increase%20representation%20on%20the%20ramp%20are%20much%20more%20cosmetic%20than%20constructive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20pretentious%20malpractices%2C%20she%20says%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20major%20fashion%20events%20is%20known%20for%20giving%20out%20generic%20casting%20calls%20that%20encourage%20models%20of%20all%20looks%2C%20genders%2C%20and%20ethnicities%20to%20upload%20their%20photos%20and%20videos%20with%20the%20event%20hashtag.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20bother%20to%20see%20these%20videos%20that%20are%20uploaded%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20lived%20experience.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20struggle%20for%20our%20spots%2C%20but%20giving%20us%20false%20hopes%20is%20just%20cruel%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20fashion%20diversity%20landscape%20is%20slowly%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFashion%20designer%20Sabyasachi%20Mukherjee%20has%20on%20many%20occasions%20set%20high%20benchmarks%20for%20inclusion%20and%20diversity%20in%20Indian%20fashion.%20From%20introducing%20plus-sized%20models%20to%20giving%20opportunities%20to%20unconventional%20beauties%2C%20Mukherjee%20has%20made%20a%20name%20for%20his%20originality.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatimes.com%2Ftrending%2Fsocial-relevance%2Fsabyasachi-faces-backlash-over-sad-looking-model-599055.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSabyasachi%2520campaign%2520trolled%2520for%2520model%2520appearing%2520sad%2C-sabyasachiofficialVerified%26amp%3Btext%3DAlthough%2520it%2527s%2520not%2520exactly%2520common%2Crecent%2520campaigns%2520looked%2520particularly%2520sad.%5C%22%3Erecent%20controversy%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20was%20trolled%20for%20an%20unsmiling%20model%2C%20also%20demonstrates%20his%20bold%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20designers%20who%20have%20done%20considerable%20work%20in%20increasing%20marginalised%20representation%20in%20Indian%20fashion%20include%20Manish%20Malhotra%2C%20Shivan%20and%20Narresh%2C%20Kunal%20Rawal%2C%20and%20Pallavi%20Mohan.%20Brands%20like%20Freakins%2C%20Zivame%2C%20Puma%2C%20Nykaa%2C%20Titan%20Raga%2C%20Vulgar%2C%20Fenty%2C%20Yeezy%2C%20and%20others%2C%20have%20joined%20the%20inclusivity%20bandwagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGauthami%20Jeji%2C%20a%20bisexual%20Indian%20model%20with%20vitiligo%20skin%20disorder%2C%20says%20that%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20Indian%20fashion.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20the%20stagnation%20in%20fashion%20standards%20and%20audience%20boredom%20prompted%20designers%2C%20producers%2C%20and%20agencies%20to%20explore%20new%20looks.%20Her%20skin%20condition%20has%20been%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%2C%20leading%20to%20casting%20calls%20since%20she%20was%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVitiligo%20has%20certainly%20given%20me%20an%20edge%20but%20my%20position%20in%20the%20industry%20will%20be%20sustained%20because%20I%20am%20very%20good%20at%20what%20I%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20She%20further%20points%20out%20the%20need%20for%20honest%20representation.%20She%20adds%20that%20celebrating%20diversity%20and%20capitalising%20on%20a%20disorder%20are%20two%20very%20different%20things.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20faced%20tokenism%20personally%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20for%20one%20shoot%20they%20take%20unique%20models%20and%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20employ%20them%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJeji%20believes%20that%20for%20things%20to%20change%2C%20the%20marginalised%20representation%20must%20be%20honest%20and%20transparent.%20Only%20then%20can%20beauty%20adapt%20to%20new%20standards%20organically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2.jpg%20933w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGauthami%20Jeji.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20world%20where%20models%20are%20called%20models%2C%20not%20plus-sized%20or%20trans%20models.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20call%20doctors%20plus-sized%20doctors%2C%20do%20we%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Sharma%2C%20the%20solution%20lies%20in%20raising%20awareness%20about%20body%20positivity%20and%20highlighting%20inspiring%20stories%20about%20fashion%20professionals%20who%20have%20overcome%20biases%20and%20are%20successful%20irrespective%20of%20how%20they%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUma%20looks%20forward%20to%20fashion%20being%20recontextualized%20as%20just%20another%20career%20path%2C%20and%20not%20a%20tool%20for%20cosmetic%20validation.%20Attaching%20glamour%20and%20self-worth%20to%20fashion%20makes%20it%20exploitative%20and%20unnecessarily%20overrated.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20only%20validation%20we%20need%20is%20our%20own.%20If%20modelling%20is%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20give%20it%20your%20100%25%2C%20confidently.%20If%20it%20works%20out%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20great%2C%20if%20it%20does%20not%2C%20keep%20your%20options%20open!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ci%3ESreemanti%20Sengupta%20is%20a%20Kolkata-based%20freelance%20writer%2C%20poet%2C%20and%20media%20studies%20lecturer.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696320008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03130652%2Fimage-1369.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbody-positivity-is-the-solution-to-tokenist-inclusion-in-the-indian-fashion-industry-say-models%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20fashion%20is%20still%20suffering%20from%20the%20patriarchal%20mindset%20where%20the%20male%20gaze%20allows%20only%20fair%2C%20slim%2C%20and%20tall%20models%20to%20be%20appreciated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbody-positivity-is-the-solution-to-tokenist-inclusion-in-the-indian-fashion-industry-say-models%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NIA%20Conducts%20Coordinated%20Raids%20on%20Rights%20Activists%20Across%2062%20Locations%20in%20Andhra%2C%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06145703%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Officials%20of%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20(NIA)%20arrived%20in%20groups%20of%20four%20and%20five%20in%2062%20locations%20across%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20on%20October%202%2C%20in%20coordinated%20raids%20at%20the%20homes%20of%20human%20rights%20activists%20and%20researchers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20raid%20teams%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20of%20NIA%20officers%20from%20Delhi%20and%20the%20local%20police%20%E2%80%93%20arrived%20between%205.30%20am%20and%206%20am%20on%20the%20day%2C%20and%20stayed%20at%20the%20locations%20till%20afternoon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20raid%20was%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20house%20of%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20and%20rights%20activist%20Durba%20Suresh%20Kumar.%20Suresh%2C%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Lawyer%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20NIA%20sleuths.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20officers.%20They%20had%20flown%20down%2C%20along%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epanch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20witnesses.%20But%20the%20local%20police%20were%20not%20informed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20said.%20The%20local%20police%2C%20Suresh%20says%2C%20joined%20much%20later.%20From%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20the%20NIA%20seized%20his%20phone%20and%20a%2012-page%20pamphlet%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20War%20Group%2C%20dating%20back%20to%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20says%20for%20the%20longest%20period%2C%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20raid%20and%20the%20exact%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20it%20was%20being%20conducted.%20The%20NIA%20later%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20ongoing%20raids%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CMunchingiputtu%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20conspiracy%20case%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20similar%20raids%20were%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20many%20rights%20activists%20and%20academics%20in%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20was%20served%20a%20notice%20under%20section%20160%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20present%20before%20the%20NIA%20as%20a%20witness.%20This%2C%20Suresh%20points%20out%2C%20is%20both%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunethical%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20counsel%20for%20many%20persons%20named%20in%20the%20case.%20I%20represent%20them%20in%20the%20high%20court%20and%20now%20the%20NIA%20wants%20me%20to%20appear%20before%20them%20as%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20a%20phone%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20lawyer%20has%20been%20named%20an%20accused%20or%20asked%20to%20be%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%20they%20have%20appeared%20as%20counsel%20in%2C%20before%20a%20court.%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20a%20Nagpur-based%20lawyer%20and%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20was%20also%20made%20an%20accused%20in%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20in%20which%20he%20had%20defended%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20conflict-affected%20Vidarbha%20region%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHRF%20functionaries%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2062%20locations%20raided%2C%2053%20are%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20nine%20are%20in%20Telangana.%20Along%20with%20the%20raids%20on%20October%202%2C%20the%20NIA%20also%20arrested%20one%20Chandra%20Narasimhulu%2C%20allegedly%20a%20state%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20the%20Pragathiseela%20Karmika%20Samakya%20(PKS)%2C%20an%20alleged%20front%20organisation%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20Narasimhulu%20was%20arrested%20from%20Satya%20Sai%20district%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Along%20with%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20a%20pistol%2C%2014%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%2C%20and%20Rs%2013%20lakhs%20in%20a%20case%20from%20another%20spot%20in%20Kadapa%20district.%20Maoist%20literature%20and%20pamphlets%20were%20also%20seized%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20those%20raided%20were%20unsure%20if%20they%20are%20being%20looked%20at%20as%20suspects%20or%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20house%20of%20K.%20Sudha%2C%20a%20state%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20was%20also%20raided.%20Sudha%2C%20who%20reaches%20at%20a%20state%20law%20university%2C%20said%20the%20NIA%20has%20taken%20her%20phone%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20raids%20took%20place%20at%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20V.S.%20Krishna%2C%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20HRF%E2%80%99s%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20units%20reached%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20residence.%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20raided%20in%202021%20in%20the%20same%20case.%20Krishna%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20got%20calls%20from%20two%20other%20HRF%20members%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20NIA%20broke%20into%20their%20houses%20because%20they%20were%20not%20home%20when%20officials%20arrived.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20contacting%20other%20members.%20When%20Sudha%20did%20not%20pick%20up%20the%20call%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20NIA%20had%20reached%20her%20place%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20other%20person%E2%80%99s%20whose%20houses%20were%20raided%20when%20they%20were%20away%20are%20HRF%E2%80%99s%20AP%20state%20general%20secretary%20Y.%20Rajesh%20in%20Amalapuram%20and%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20state%20vice-president%20K.V.%20Jagannadha%20Rao%20in%20Srikakulam.%20Rajesh%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20back%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20him%20late%20on%20October%202%2C%20said%20that%20the%20NIA%20contacted%20him%20a%20little%20before%206%20am.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20came%20with%20a%20notice%20under%20Section%20165%20(2)%20of%20the%20CrPc%2C%20which%20authorised%20them%20to%20search%20the%20premise.%20Some%20of%20my%20neighbours%20went%20to%20my%20place%20and%20the%20NIA%20conducted%20the%20raid%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajesh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20NIA%20has%20not%20made%20any%20seizures%20from%20his%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBooks%2C%20vernacular%20literature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20from%20another%20HRF%20functionary%E2%80%99s%20place%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20picked%20up%20over%2060%20books.%20Sudha%2C%20who%20shared%20information%20about%20the%20raid%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20basically%20picked%20up%20every%20book%20and%20document%20that%20had%20red%20font%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said%20the%20officers%20did%20not%20know%20to%20read%20Telugu.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20books%20and%20our%20write-ups%20are%20in%20the%20local%20language.%20They%20mindlessly%20picked%20things%20up%20and%20later%20call%20it%20incriminating%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20HRF%20and%20IAPL%2C%20houses%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Civil%20Liberties%20Committee%20(CLC)%2C%20the%20Committee%20for%20the%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%20(CRPP)%2C%20and%20the%20Revolutionary%20Writers%20Association%20(RWA)%2C%20were%20also%20raided%20among%20others.%20The%20NIA%20has%20accused%20veteran%20rights%20activists%20and%20organisations%20of%20acting%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfronts%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20organisation%2C%20banned%20in%202009.%20This%20claim%20has%20been%20vehemently%20opposed%20by%20rights%20organisations.%20HRF%20has%20called%20the%20NIA%E2%80%99s%20claim%20%E2%80%9Ca%20plain%20canard%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CSeeking%20to%20criminalise%20our%20human%20rights%20activity%20will%20never%20succeed.%20HRF%20is%20not%20an%20appendage%20of%20the%20Maoists%20or%20any%20other%20political%20party.%20HRF%20was%20formed%20on%20October%2011%2C%201998%20and%20we%20have%20turned%2025%20this%20month.%20We%20shall%20persist%20in%20spreading%20a%20human%20rights%20culture%20in%20society%20with%20the%20certitude%20that%20a%20broad-based%20and%20truly%20independent%20human%20rights%20movement%20is%20desirable%20and%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20HRF%20said%2C%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20released%20earlier%20today%2C%20October%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20locations%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20subjected%20to%20raids%20are%20in%20Guntur%2C%20Palanadu%2C%20Vijayawada%2C%20Rajhmundry%2C%20Prakasam%2C%20Bapatla%2C%20Eluru%2C%20East%20Godawari%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20Konasema%2C%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Vizianagaram%2C%20Nellore%2C%20Tirupati%2C%20Kadapa%2C%20Anantpur%2C%20and%20Kurnool%20districts.%20The%20NIA%20said%20that%20the%20nine%20locations%20in%20Telangana%20include%20districts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Mahabubnagar%2C%20Hanumakonda%2C%20Ranga%20Reddy%2C%20and%20Adilabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20investigation%2C%20first%20registered%20and%20handled%20by%20the%20local%20state%20police%20in%202020%2C%20was%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%202021.%20Popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Munchingiputtu%20case%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20deals%20with%20alleged%20Maoist%20movement%20and%20literature%20in%20a%20village%20of%20the%20Alluri%20Sitharama%20Raju%3Cbr%3E%20district.%20The%20NIA%20has%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20seven%20persons%20in%20that%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20immediate%20causes%20for%20worry%20expressed%20by%20those%20raided%20is%20around%20the%20seizure%20of%20electronic%20devices.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20lawyers%20and%20researchers%20and%20very%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20their%20electronic%20devices%20for%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CSeizure%20of%20electronic%20devices%20including%20mobiles%20without%20even%20providing%20cloned%20copies%20to%20the%20owners%20amounts%20to%20immediate%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20precious%20work-related%20material%20and%20contacts.%20It%20leads%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20HRF%20statement%20reads.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20confiscate%20these%20devices%20in%20such%20a%20sudden%20manner%20results%20in%20a%20stunning%20dispossession.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20deprival%20of%20valuable%20property%20of%20the%20functionaries%20concerned%20but%20also%20of%20their%20right%20to%20livelihood%2C%20privacy%20and%20human%20dignity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06145703%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20raids%20were%20in%20connection%20with%20the%202021%20Munchingiputtu%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20conspiracy%20case.%20Devices%20and%20literature%20belonging%20to%20functionaries%20and%20lawyers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People's%20Lawyer%20and%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20along%20with%20various%20other%20rights%20bodies%20were%20seized.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WB%20ups%20India's%20FY24%2