p%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fashion%20industry%2C%20Ribhav%20notes%20that%20wastage%20exists%20at%20each%20stage%20from%20product%20designing%20to%20development%20and%20scaled%20production.%20Huge%20proportions%20of%20waste%20are%20generated%20to%20maximise%20profits%2C%20particularly%20during%20scaled%20production%2C%20to%20save%20time%20and%20costs%20per%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20leather%20is%20infamous%20for%20being%20bad%20for%20the%20environment.%20But%20what%20about%20scrap%20that%20is%20already%20present%20and%20available%3F%20My%20vision%20was%20to%20use%20this%20waste%20leather%20to%20make%20luxury%20products%2C%20and%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20we%20came%20up%20with%20our%20first%20collection%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.econock.com%2Fpages%2Fsophisticated-survivor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESophisticated%20Survivor%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20Econock%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ribhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20source%20material%20Econock%20employs%20is%20leather%20scraps%20which%20are%20oddly%20shaped%20and%20sized.%20They%20are%20mostly%20remains%20and%20cut-outs%20of%20larger%20leather%20skins.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Nora%20Tote%20Bag%20from%20our%20Sophisticated%20Survivor%20collection.%20The%20base%20is%20made%20out%20of%20waste%20leather.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20two%20halves%20on%20the%20surface%20are%20created%20from%20a%20single%20sheet%20of%20leather%20with%20the%20positive%20part%20placed%20on%20the%20upper%20panel%20and%20the%20remaining%20waste%20utilised%20in%20the%20bottom%20sections%20so%20that%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263620%2Ffarmse-farms-on-wheels-organic-zero-waste-store-ahmedabad-organic-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezer